function Start(snoQuest, idActorFollower)
	local actorMonkFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Frac_Prologue_Monk_Follower")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorMonkFollower) then
		Hydra.ActorDisableAI(actorMonkFollower)
		Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(convMonkFlw00, actorMonkFollower, true)
		Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(convMonkFlw00)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(actorMonkFollower)
	end

end
